(deftitle "Probability Book Recommendation")

(defpara "For those wanting to learn probability, I heartily
recommend " (deflink "http://www.amazon.com" "DeGroot and
Schervish") ".")

(defpara "I sat in on a class that
used " (deflink "http://www.amazon.com" "Ross") ", but (modulo
the latter statistics half of M&S that Ross does not cover) I
found the language in M&S to be more crisp and concise. I felt it
was easier to find and extract the key points from it.")